Project outputs:
- Inter-ministerial arrangements and legislation harmonization;
- National Response System Improvement;
- Preparedness for Disaster Response

Project outputs:
- Improving community stabilization and strengthening national and local capacities to effectively engage in early recovery coordination, planning and implementation;
- Strengthening disaster risk reduction and climate risk management; 
- The 8 point agenda and gender empowerment as a cross-cutting area.

Project outputs:
- ER capacity development of main stakeholders, awareness raising, advocacy and improvement of ER coordination and partnership of REACT groups in Tajikistan, development of REACT ER coordination capacities;
- Implementation of ER projects at local level in the disaster and mine/UXO affected communities;
- Mine/EOD capacity building of the Committee of Emergency Situation and Civil Defence;
- Strengthen Government and civil society capacities for conflict prevention and social cohesion at a local, regional and national level

